    "description": "BroadBand Security, Inc. provides IT security services in Japan. The company offers security consulting and CSIRT construction/operation support; risk assessment, virus infection check, and network device configuration diagnosis; PCI DSS compliance support/PCI DSS compliance on-site assessment, as well as ISO27001 certification/privacy mark acquisition support; and targeted attack email training and vulnerability information provision services. It also provides web application vulnerability, network vulnerability, smartphone application vulnerability, software quality analysis, SaaS type software quality automatic analysis diagnosis services; and website content tampering detection and daily automatic vulnerability diagnosis. In addition, the company offers emergency response, digital forensics, Internet isolation cloud, managed security, malware detection, SIEM construction and analysis, splunk automatic blocking integration, and secure email services. BroadBand Security, Inc. was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan."
